<PLACE form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:208561573" id="Pl-68" type="RGN">West</PLACE> was able to carve up <PLACE country="CN" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:18099327" id="Pl-56" latLong="35.000°N 105.000°E" type="COUNTRY">China</PLACE> into &quot;Spheres of Influence&quot;, and was able
