<PLACE country="CN" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:18099327" id="Pl-58" latLong="35.000°N 105.000°E" type="COUNTRY">China</PLACE> proper in 1936. It was a war that <PLACE country="JP" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:19768770" id="Pl-35" latLong="36.000°N 138.000°E" type="COUNTRY">Japan</PLACE> assumed would be ended
